sql_query.sql: SELECT "users"."id" FROM "users" WHERE "users"."active" = TRUE AND "users"."staged" = FALSE AND (suspended_till IS NULL OR suspended_till <= '2020-05-28 18:58:06.960995') AND "users"."username_lower" = 'a' LIMIT 20

SELECT "users"."id" FROM "users" LEFT OUTER JOIN "user_search_data" ON "user_search_data"."user_id" = "users"."id" WHERE "users"."active" = TRUE AND "users"."staged" = FALSE AND (suspended_till IS NULL OR suspended_till <= '2020-05-28 18:58:06.965668') AND (user_search_data.search_data @@ TO_TSQUERY('simple', '''a'':*')) ORDER BY CASE WHEN username_lower LIKE 'a%' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ASC, last_seen_at DESC LIMIT 20
